column3: “It's a cougher, but well worth it. A very nice, whimsical high that hits you right away and makes things feel a little extra sweet and clear without rendering you unable to function. Panera Bread tastes hella good right now.”

“Here is the second of six strains that I received from a wonderful old friend in Lake Tahoe, Nevada.  

Stardawg Alien is A hybrid Sativa of Stardawg x Alien Kush.  A favoured strain in Lake Tahoe I hear from my friend.  This strain has a rather musty note, but it is not a fault I hear.  One of its parent strains is a very musty nosed semence not unlike a slight diesel note, but not over-powering as a full note.  Thi...”
“One of my fave strains! The flavor of the flower is amazing!”
“just got this strain 10 mins ago nd well it's 🔥🔥🔥🔥”
“Distinct scent, smokes nicely, hard to find but very good :)”

“One star says it...I did not like this cannabis.  It made me feel heavy headed, like I was carrying a burden instead of a buzz.  I was not paranoid or anxious, nothing like that.  I was not happy, spacey, creative...I just felt serious.  I have tried ASD for the past few days in a variety of situations and it was the same feeling...like my head was wrapped up too tight in a beanie.  Some folks might like that feeling...”
